      "category": "researcher",
      "content": "1) Go to this website : https://ucp.nordvpn.com/lost-password\n2) Enter your main account (main@main.com)\n3) Go to main@main.com mail adress and copy the link\n4) Open in your browser.\n5) Now lets chat with your support to changing mail request\n6) After great chat with Claudia and Marcus (Cheers!) They changed my email from \"main@main.com\" to \"main2@main2.com\"\n7) Go to step 4 and Enter new password.\n8) Password will be changed!",
